'''Amirmohammad Razzaghinia''' ({{langx|fa|امیرمحمد رزاقی‌نیا}}; born 11 April 2006) is an Iranian [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder (association football)|defender]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] team [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]], and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].

==Youth career==
===KIA Football Academy===
Born in [[Yazd]], Razzaghinia was recruited to the country's most prestigious football academy, [[KIA Football Academy]], where he progressed through the ranks to eventually  play in [[League 2 (Iran)|League 2]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/2351818/%D8%B1%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%82%DB%8C-%D9%86%DB%8C%D8%A7-%D8%AC%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D9%BE%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D8%B2%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%84%D9%87%DB%8C-%D8%B1%D8%A7-%D9%86%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%87-%D9%85%DB%8C-%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%AF|title=رزاقی‌نیا جای پای عزت‌اللهی را نشانه می‌رود|website=varzesh3.com}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Gol Gohar===
Razzaghinia signed for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] side [[Gol Gohar Sirjan F.C.|Gol Gohar]] on a free transfer in 2024.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://footballi.net/news/r/864237/%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%87-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C-%D9%86%D9%88%D8%AC%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%DA%A9%D8%B4%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D9%87-%DA%AF%D9%84-%DA%AF%D9%87%D8%B1-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA|title=ستاره تیم ملی نوجوانان کشور به گل‌گهر پیوست|website=footballi.net|language=fa}}</ref> He played 23 games in the league, scoring 2 goals.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fbref.com/en/players/ac3242eb/matchlogs/2024-2025/Amirmohammad-Razaghinia-Match-Logs|title=Amirmohammad Razzaghinia-2024/25 Match Logs|website=fbref.com}}</ref>

===Esteghlal===
The following season, Razzaghinia signed for [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/2132726/%D9%81%D9%88%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%BE%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%87-%D9%84%DB%8C%DA%AF-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%B1-%D8%B1%D8%A7-%D8%AE%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AF|title=فوری: استقلال پدیده لیگ برتر را خرید|website=varzesh3.com|language=fa}}</ref> He made 21 appearances in the [[2025–26 Persian Gulf Pro League|league]], before the season was suspended due to the [[2026 Iran war]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://iranwire.com/en/features/151545-league-suspended-by-security-order-irgc-counts-on-world-cup-for-war/|title=League Suspended by Security Order; IRGC Counts on World Cup for War|website=iranwire.com}}</ref>

==International career==
Razzaghinia has been a part of several youth national teams for [[Iran]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mehrnews.com/news/5769372/%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3%D8%AA-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85-%D9%81%D9%88%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%86%D9%88%D8%AC%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%B4%D8%AF|title=لیست بازیکنان تیم فوتبال نوجوانان ایران اعلام شد|website=mehrnews.com|language=fa}}</ref>

He was a part of the [[Iran national under-17 football team|Iran U17]] [[2023 FIFA U-17 World Cup squads#Group C#Iran|squad]] for the [[2023 FIFA U-17 World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fdp.fifa.org/assetspublic/ce115/pdf/SquadLists-English.pdf|title=Squad Lists–English|website=fdp.fifa.org}}</ref> He made 8 appearances for the U17 team, scoring 5 goals, including a brace against Belarus.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/481633/Iran-U17-beat-Belarus-U16-at-Development-Cup|title=Iran U17 beat Belarus U16 at "Development Cup"|website=tehrantimes.com}}</ref> Razzaghinia has also represented [[Iran national under-20 football team|Iran U20]], and [[Iran national under-23 football team|Iran U23]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/517515/Iran-start-2026-AFC-U23-Asian-Cup-qualification-on-high|title=Iran start 2026 AFC U23 Asian Cup qualification on high|website=tehrantimes.com}}</ref>

Razzaghinia was included in the [[Iran national football team|Iran]] senior squad for their final[[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – AFC third round|qualifying]] match against [[North Korea national football team|North Korea]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/710515/north-korea-iran|title=Iran 3–0 North Korea|website=espn.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/en/match-centre/match/520/288263/288276/400018435|title=Iran 3–0 North Korea|website=fifa.com}}</ref> Razzaghinia was included in Iran's preliminary squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.si.com/soccer/iran-2026-world-cup-preview|title=Iran 2026 World Cup preview|website=Sports Illustrated}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/en/tournaments/mens/worldcup/canadamexicousa2026/articles/ir-iran-squad-named|title=Ghalenoei names preliminary Iran squad|website=fifa.com}}</ref>

